    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Rise and shine! Before you begin\u2026</strong></p><p>Whipping this up for breakfast? Some of this recipe can be prepped ahead (if you like!)</p><p>Make step 2 the night before and store in an airtight container, then finish the rest in the morning, and enjoy within 24 hours</p><p>Skim through these steps and get all your equipment ready</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cherry-bakewell-pancakes/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cherry-bakewell-pancakes/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add your <strong>flaked almonds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p><p>Once toasted, transfer to a bowl and reserve the pan \u2013 these are your <strong>toasted almonds</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cherry-bakewell-pancakes/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>granola </strong>and <strong>toasted almonds </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>toasted almond granola</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cherry-bakewell-pancakes/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>cr\u00e8me fra\u00eeche </strong>and <strong>maple syrup </strong>in a small bowl \u2013 this is your <strong>sweet cream</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cherry-bakewell-pancakes/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>buttermilk pancakes</strong> to a plate and pop in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 30 secs on high or until warmed through</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cherry-bakewell-pancakes/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>warmed pancakes </strong>with the <strong>sweet cream</strong>, <strong>cherry sauce </strong>and <strong>toasted almond granola </strong>\u2013 these are your <strong>cherry bakewell pancakes</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cherry-bakewell-pancakes/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cherry bakewell pancakes </strong>or box up to enjoy on-the-go</p><p>Time to start your day!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
